title: Premium has lots of bugs
text:
I have the premium subscription and have had it for 5 + years. It‚Äôs always been great and I use it every day.

On a lesser note, random videos get downloaded. Id understand if it were videos that I watch all the time, but sometimes they‚Äôre super random. Idk, I don‚Äôt think it‚Äôs a bug, it‚Äôs just the algorithm I‚Äôm sure. Not a super big deal, but I had to say my peace üòÇ

title: Great Most of the Time
text:
I love the convenience of the app to be able to be notified on new videos posted on my subscribed channels and can join ‚ÄúLive‚Äù chats easily from my phone. The one thing that happens often though out of the blue, is when trying to post a comment, it hangs and buffers in the comment field below the video. VERY frustrating and I have read a common occurrence. Any fixes I Googled don‚Äôt work although once I cleared all my cookies and that helped. Once. Please YouTube! Fix this annoying bug/glitch!!
UPDATE 3/17/2024
This still is happening and it can‚Äôt be all my subscriptions are suddenly monitoring my comments. Secondly all the video descriptions during the day are whited out as well as comments. At night there are only black backgrounds with handles showing up in blue. If I hold my finger on the screen where a comment or description should be visible, it shows up and the once I release my finger tip it goes back to black. I have re installed the app, turned my phone off and back on and no changes. Taking away one star.
